"elaborazione dalla console Python."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterconversion.rst:124
msgid "PCT to RGB"
msgstr "Da PCT a RGB"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterconversion.rst:125
msgid ""
"Converts an 8 bit paletted image to a 24 bit RGB. It will convert a "
"pseudocolor band from the input file to an RGB file of the desired format."
msgstr ""
"Converte un'immagine palettata a 8 bit in una RGB a 24 bit. Converte una "
"banda di pseudocolore dal file in ingresso in un file RGB del formato "
"desiderato."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasterconversion.rst:129
msgid ""
"This algorithm is derived from the `GDAL pct2rgb utility "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/pct2rgb.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Questo algoritmo è derivato da `GDAL pct2rgb utility "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/pct2rgb.html>`_."

